name: Cathay Pacific 777-367ER [B-KQO] Landing at Vancouver Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Another upload from Vancouver! YVR is such a fun airport to spot at. Here we have one of Cathay Pacific's two daily flights into Vancouver, Flight 838 arriving on Runway 26R from Hong Kong. This video of Cathay Pacific is dedicated to CathayA340, a spotting channel from New York City, featuring content from New York JFK and EWR. The link is below. Enjoy the video, and have patience, more Tokyo stuff is coming soon!

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
